---
const status = [
  "Web online",
  "SSL zabezpečeno",
  "Zálohy připravené",
  "Monitoring aktivní",
];
---

<header id="top" class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 pb-12 pt-14 sm:px-6 md:pb-16 md:pt-24">
  <div class="mb-8 flex items-center gap-3.5 text-ink-soft md:mb-12 reveal">
    <span class="h-px w-10 bg-ink-soft"></span>
    <span class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] sm:text-xs">Weby, hosting a péče pro malé firmy a živnostníky</span>
  </div>

  <h1 class="display text-[clamp(40px,9.5vw,138px)] font-light leading-[0.95] tracking-tight reveal">
    Váš podnik<br />
    <em class="font-normal italic">online</em> - <span class="relative whitespace-nowrap">bez<span class="absolute bottom-[0.06em] left-0 h-[0.055em] w-full bg-ink"></span></span><br />
    technického <span class="text-pine">stresu.</span>
  </h1>

  <div class="mt-9 grid gap-8 border-t border-line pt-7 md:mt-12 md:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr] md:items-start md:gap-12">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="max-w-[46ch] text-lg text-ink-soft">
        Vytvořím Vám moderní web, zařídím doménu, hosting i zálohy a pomůžu
        s nastavením firemního e-mailu podle potřeby - a pak se o všechno průběžně
        starám. Vy se věnujete zákazníkům, techniku nechte na mně.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-7 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap">
        <a
          href="#contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-pine px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-paper transition-colors hover:bg-pine-deep"
        >
          Nezávazná konzultace zdarma
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a
          href="#cenik"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-ink px-6 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-ink transition-colors hover:bg-ink hover:text-paper"
        >
          Podívat se na nabídku
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- living "care system" status card -->
    <div class="grain-card rounded-2xl border border-line bg-paper/70 p-5 reveal sm:p-6">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-line pb-3">
        <span class="font-mono text-[10.5px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-ink-soft">Stav vašeho webu</span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 font-mono text-[10.5px] uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-pine">
          <span class="status-dot"></span> Vše v pořádku
        </span>
      </div>
      <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2.5">
        {status.map((s) => (
          <li class="flex items-center justify-between font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-ink">
            <span class="flex items-center gap-2.5">
              <svg class="text-pine" width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
              {s}
            </span>
            <span class="text-pine-soft">OK</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- trust strip -->
<div class="border-y border-line bg-paper-deep/40">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-3 gap-y-1.5 px-5 py-4 text-center font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-ink-soft sm:gap-x-4 sm:px-6 sm:text-xs">
    {["Web", "Doména", "E-mail", "Hosting", "Zálohy", "Údržba"].map((t, i) => (
      <>
        {i > 0 && <span class="text-pine" aria-hidden="true">·</span>}
        <span>{t}</span>
      </>
    ))}
  </div>
</div>
